extendedInfo.description: Fancy Jigsaw is a classic puzzle game. Drag the Sailing.pieces to the right place to re-establish the full picture. Don't sweat it if you are unable to solve the puzzle easily. You can use the peek button to preview the original image.There are 100 levels in this game. The further you advance, the more challenging the puzzle becomes. This app also allows you to save the Sailing to your SD .Sailing is a mark of human being fight with nature. The history of sailing is as far as human civilization. In this series you may find modern sailing for sports championship, as well as ancient multi-mast sailing, all in high quality hand-paintings. Really worth a try.Cool Features Include:- More than 100 pictures of Sailing.- Multiple difficulty levels (from 3*3 to the most difficult 7*7).- Save to phone album function.- Images gallery and difficulty selection.Fancy JigSaw is suitable for a wide range of audiences, Many different modes and pictures in the game will keep you excited and entertained for a long time.Keywords:puzzle,puzzles,Jigsaw,games,brainfun,funny, Sailing,entertainment,wallpapers
